=Create VTN Flow Filter Entry=
This operation is used to create a VTN Flow Filter Entry.

==Request==
{|class = "wikitable"
|-
|Method || POST
|-
|Request URI || 
* XML format
 /vtns/{vtn_name}/flowfilters/{ff_type}/flowfilterentries.xml
* JSON format
 /vtns/{vtn_name}/flowfilters/{ff_type}/flowfilterentries.json
|-
|Request body ||
* XML format
 <flowfilterentry seqnum="{seqnum}"
  fl_name="{fl_name}"
  action_type="{action_type}"
  nmg_name="{nmg_name}" priority="{priority}"
  dscp="{dscp}" />
* JSON format
 {
 "flowfilterentry": {
      "seqnum": "{seqnum}",
      "fl_name": "{fl_name}",
      "action_type": "{action_type}",
      "nmg_name": "{nmg_name}",
      "priority": "{priority}",
      "dscp": "{dscp}"
      }
  }
|}


